Title: Google admits anti-competitive conduct involving Google Search in Australia
Description: The ACCC has today commenced Federal Court proceedings against Google Asia Pacific over anti-competitive understandings that Google admits it reached in the past with Telstra and Optus regarding the pre-installation of Google Search on Android mobile phones.

Title: Hyperclay | Single-file HTML apps
Description: A single HTML file is all you need to build a web app. Hyperclay hosts these HTML files so you can create personal, malleable software easily.

Title: Secure Boot, TPM and Anti-Cheat Engines
Description: Anti-cheat engines are now requiring users to have Secure Boot and a fTPM enabled in order to play online multiplayer games. Will this decrease the amount of cheating, or is it a futile attempt at curbing an ever-growing problem?

Title: When Did AI Take Over Hacker News? | Blog | Zach Perkel
